oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The general topic of this meeting is “General Metabolic Disorders, their Diagnosis and Treatment.” I will talk briefly on the subject of polioencephalomalacia and its relationship to thiamine metabolism, but my emphasis will probably be in the field of diagnosis.
